<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Convite para liga</title>
  </head>

  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #0f172a; height: 100%;">
    <table
      width="100%"
      height="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      role="presentation"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center" valign="middle">
          <table
            width="100%"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="
              max-width: 480px;
              background-color: #111827;
              border-radius: 16px;
              padding: 32px;
              color: #f9fafb;
              font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            "
          >
            <tr>
              <td align="center">
                <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #f97316;">
                  Convite para participar de liga
                </h2>

                <p style="color: #e5e7eb;">
                  Olá, <strong><%= @user.name.presence || @user.email %></strong>
                </p>

                <p style="color: #e5e7eb; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Você recebeu um convite de
                  <strong><%= @invited_by.name.presence || @invited_by.email %></strong>
                  para participar da liga
                  <strong><%= @liga.nome %></strong>.
                </p>

                <p style="color: #e5e7eb; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Entre na plataforma para visualizar o convite e decidir se deseja participar.
                </p>

                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 24px 0;">
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      align="center"
                      style="
                        background-color: #f97316;
                        border-radius: 999px;
                      "
                    >
                      <a
                        href="<%= liga_url(@liga) %>"
                        style="
                          display: inline-block;
                          padding: 14px 28px;
                          font-weight: bold;
                          text-decoration: none;
                          color: #111827;
                        "
                      >
                        Ver convite da liga
                      </a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; line-height: 1.5;">
                  Caso você não reconheça esse convite, basta ignorar este e-mail.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>